d not greying the lines.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> yet you go on to say <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Nothing worse than a person running in and taking your spawned mob after your group spent an hour or more clearing it's PH's<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
